{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-077-078-terrible-toothache",
    "title": "Lesson 77: Terrible toothache",
    "audioFilename": "077&078－Terrible Toothache.mp3",
    "duration": 97.097,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.27,
      "end": 4.95,
      "text": "Lesson 77–Terrible Toothache.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第77课——要命的牙痛。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s001a",
      "start": 6.52,
      "end": 10.8,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s001b",
      "start": 12.2,
      "end": 18.54,
      "text": "What time of day is it, do you think? How do you know?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你认为当时是一天中的什么时间？你是怎么知道的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s001c",
      "start": 20.88,
      "end": 23.92,
      "text": "Good morning, Mr. Croft.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "早上好，克罗夫特先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s001d",
      "start": 24.92,
      "end": 30.44,
      "text": "Good morning, nurse. I want to see the dentist, please.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "早上好，护士。我想见牙医。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 32.06,
      "end": 33.44,
      "text": "Do you have an appointment?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您预约了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 34.56,
      "end": 36.24,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "没有。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 36.62,
      "end": 37.76,
      "text": "Is it urgent?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "很紧急吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 38.68,
      "end": 40.52,
      "text": "Yes, it is.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "是的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 41.32,
      "end": 43.2,
      "text": "It's very urgent.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "非常紧急。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 44.24,
      "end": 45.98,
      "text": "I feel awful.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我难受极了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 46.76,
      "end": 49.62,
      "text": "I have a terrible toothache.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我牙痛得要命。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 50.86,
      "end": 53.34,
      "text": "Can you come at 10 a.m.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您能在上午十点来吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 53.44,
      "end": 56.06,
      "text": "on Monday, April 24th?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "4月24日，星期一。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 57.06,
      "end": 61.52,
      "text": "I must see the dentist now, nurse.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "护士，我现在就必须见牙医。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 62.74,
      "end": 66.5,
      "text": "The dentist is very busy at the moment.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "牙医此刻很忙。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 67.42,
      "end": 70.54,
      "text": "Can you come at 2 p.m.?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您下午两点来可以吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 71.06,
      "end": 73.2,
      "text": "That's very late.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那太晚了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 74.3,
      "end": 76.64,
      "text": "Can the dentist see me now?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "牙医现在能给我看吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 77.34,
      "end": 80.72,
      "text": "I'm afraid that he can't, Mr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "恐怕不能，克罗夫特"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 81.1,
      "end": 81.42,
      "text": "Croft.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 82.1,
      "end": 84.94,
      "text": "Can't you wait till this afternoon?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您不能等到今天下午吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 86.06,
      "end": 90.5,
      "text": "I can wait, but my toothache can't.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我能等，但我的牙痛等不了。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
